import React from 'react'; import './FAQ.css' const FAQ = () => { return(

Help & FAQs

Below are some of the most frequently asked questions about Cu-stum. To get your questios, ideas, or feedback to us the only thing you need to do is email custuminspiration@gmail.com or DM us on Instagram @cu-stum_inspiration about any topics that aren't covered here. We would love to hear from you.

What does Cu-stum do?

Cu-stum is the hope that you need when you need it. We give you the best quotes that would motivate a beginner developr to expert level developer.

How does Cu-stum process work?

Every week, we bring new quotes to the table from all positions and community. 50% of the quotes that presented each week doesn't make it to the face of the platform.

As a person that support the company, how long will it take for me to hear back from you once I message yall?

We are a small company so it make take time for us to reply back to your question, idea, or feedback. We will respond to you within 12-72 hours of your message.

Do y'all have any companies that work with y'all?

At the moment we are Cu-stum alone but in the future we plan on linking with other companies that may benefit their communtity

) } export default FAQ
